videos.description: Tyrese Haliburton drives to the basket and throws a no-look pass to Cameron Lard for a nice layup finish.
videos.headline: Haliburton's no-look pass leads to Iowa State lay-in

videos.description: Cameron Lard converts a fast-break layup for Iowa State, drawing a foul in the process.
videos.headline: Lard gets tough layup to go after he's fouled

videos.description: Iowa State takes the lead against Texas after Lindell Wigginton hits a tough and-1 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Wigginton nails an and-1 3-pointer
